Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天犒劳一下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想散散步帮助恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 要我说你不用道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然是有点受打击啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但说回来那也是自然而然的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子一点儿也没做错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我当时心里扑通扑通的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被男生说喜欢自己 任谁都会小鹿乱撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这是自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 冲仓同学？冲仓驱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感觉他有些帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不觉得他有点装腔作势吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就是 有点自我中心的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 相当自我中心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 对透子撒谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 没想跟雪告白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那只是没下定决心 还在动摇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这可不叫撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想告白的女生心跳不已下不了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这是很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以 我是觉得你这么说很奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感觉出来走走真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回去也没问题的 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去校园画鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}下次让我看看你的素描哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}唔 不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是罗吉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是 你好 乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓同学？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你这会来学校干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能坐你旁边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 嗯 当然了 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你太生分了啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说了那种话 没法再是平常的感觉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}刚才把你错认成冲仓同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我就喜欢你的那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以说 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}话说 那种地方是哪种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感觉良好又少根筋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总之你先坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}拍成电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}横幅广告上写着呢 放逐和王国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等着 我查下时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}后天有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}腿麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是不是还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 小雪 今天来学校干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为看到透子走进校门了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好了好了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样子好画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把它们赶到一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我就想到会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}米粒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是呢 感觉撒饵料太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}马上就好了 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多余的碳素笔应该在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和透子两人共处一室 我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你 很在意那个叫驱的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你刚才把我当成驱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你在等他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在潜意识里是等着他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…喜欢…冲仓同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只有我一个人的话 说不定就要糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓驱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是透子的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山柳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看你脚蛮疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}扭伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我可不认可伤成这样还要出来走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱真是个奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳 是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}用平假名写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}写成汉字就像幽灵一样了 所以用平假名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.55,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an7}日本传说在柳树下经常出现幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柔软而强韧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沉静而刚强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}马旁加区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是驾马 赶马的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说不定父母起名字的时候还想加上我缺少点什么的意思进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我觉得父母不会在孩子的名字里加这种意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快点快点 进去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那边已经下起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真好啊 乔纳森你们没什么好烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 下起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 这个 多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后啊这次的大夫 怎么看都是青涩的新人女医生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她用听诊器听我肺部的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不停地说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「好 大口吸气 好 呼出来吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前面听了四次 背后听了四次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后非常遗憾地说「您肺部的声音真悦耳呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她就那么想听我肺部不正常的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 不好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}爸爸 还是别再说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是…是这样的吗
